Citation.sTitle: Solubility of D-(-)-p-Hydroxyphenylglycine Dane Salt in Mixtures of Methanol and Ethanol
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of D-(-)-p-hydroxyphenylglycine dane salt (HPGDane Salt) in binary methanol and ethanol solvent mixtures was measured using a laser technique with a temperature range from 278.15 K to 323.15 K and a mole fraction () of methanol in original solvent range from 0.0000 to 1.0000. The results were correlated with a semiempirical equation.
